447
00:43:27,300 --> 00:43:30,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Really? What is this? It's scary.</font>

448
00:43:30,700 --> 00:43:34,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Perhaps, is it something like that? Alien?</font>

449
00:43:34,300 --> 00:43:35,300
<font color=#FFFF00>That's going a bit far.</font>

450
00:43:35,300 --> 00:43:36,900
<font color=#FFFF00>- Zombie?<br>- Vampire.</font>

451
00:43:36,960 --> 00:43:41,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Anyway, the Chief said he'll report the case at the Heart Association and the AHA</font>

452
00:43:41,230 --> 00:43:44,670
<font color=#FFFF00>and donate to the circulation of the magazine. He's really excited.</font>

453
00:43:44,670 --> 00:43:47,370
<font color=#FFFF00>I think he contacted the reporter as well.</font>

454
00:43:47,370 --> 00:43:49,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, are we being broadcasted?</font>

455
00:43:49,890 --> 00:43:51,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Just get to work.</font>

