<font color=#FFFF00>Are you alright?</font>

458
00:44:09,670 --> 00:44:13,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Hello. Did you get the pass to get out?</font>

459
00:44:15,470 --> 00:44:18,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Please be careful.</font>

